leave bckup/Asami

narrator: A few days later, he passed away quietly in that same room.
narrator: The candle had long gone out by then.

narrator: The village held a small ceremony.
narrator: People came and went.
narrator: Said kind things.
narrator: Then returned to their lives.

narrator: The house became quieter than I had ever known a house to be.
[wait time="1.0"]
audio music "res://BGM/Sea, You & Me.mp3" [fade="1.0"]

narrator: But I couldn't forget the promise.
narrator: It had weight to it.
narrator: The kind that doesn't fade.

[background arg="res://Assets/Noraneko_Backgrounds_Pack_3/Noraneko_Backgrounds_Pack_3/Temple_Spring_Afternoon.png" fade="1.5" wait="true"]
[background arg="res://Assets/Noraneko_Backgrounds_Pack_3/Noraneko_Backgrounds_Pack_3/Temple_Spring_Clouds.png" fade="1.5" wait="true"]
